## Goal
- Implement an event-sourcing based inventory management library following CQRS+ES principles.

## Constraints & Preferences
- No framework dependencies; purely in-memory implementation.
- Public API must adhere to `src/types.ts` and be exportable from `src/index.ts`.
- Prohibit direct mutation of state objects (must use spread syntax or new objects).
- Use `Object.hasOwn` for `Record` key existence checks to avoid inherited property risks (e.g., `toString`, `__proto__`).
- Ensure all domain logic is encapsulated in `decide` (Command Model) and `evolve` (Event Sourcing), and read models are handled by `StockProjection`.

