## Key Decisions
- Use `Object.hasOwn` instead of `undefined` checks for `ProductState.reservations` to prevent prototype pollution/inherited property access during event replay.
- Enforce immutable state updates in both the Command Model and Projection to prevent side effects and ensure predictability.

